Interface LearningExample.StateLocalInputMealyLearningExample<I,O>

    public static interface LearningExample.StateLocalInputMealyLearningExample<I,O>
extends LearningExample<I,StateLocalInputMealyMachine<?,I,?,O>>
    A LearningExample refinement for StateLocalInputMealyMachine.

    Note that while StateLocalInputMealyMachines can return information about their local inputs and are therefore in general partially defined, the examples are total MealyMachines in order to be usable with the existing integration-test infrastructure of (total) MealyMachines. The 'undefined' transitions are answered with getUndefinedOutput().
